messages.original:
4 groups of missiles remain. 
2 groups are flying over northern Vinnytsia Oblast towards Starokostyantyniv, Khmelnytskyi Oblast.
2 groups are flying one after another through northern Kirovohrad Oblast towards Mykolaiv Oblast.

2 groups of missiles are flying towards southern Khmelnytskyi Oblast from the northeast. 
2 groups of missiles are flying towards Pervomaisk, Mykolaiv Oblast from the north.

2 groups of missiles entered northern Mykolaiv Oblast, flying south past Pervomaisk.
1 group of missiles flew past Vovkovyntsi, Khmelnytskyi Oblast on a southwestern course.
1 group of missiles flew past Dunaivtsi, Khmelnytskyi Oblast on a western course.

2 groups of missiles are flying west through southern Khmelnytskyi Oblast towards southern Ternopil Oblast.
1 group of missiles is flying northwest through southern Vinnytsia Oblast.
1 group of missiles is flying to Vinnytsia Oblast from northern Odesa Oblast.

2 groups of missiles are flying west through southern Ternopil Oblast towards Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast.
2 groups of missiles are flying northwest through southern Vinnytsia Oblast toward southern Khmelnytskyi Oblast.

1 group of missiles is flying northwest towards Zolochiv, Lviv Oblast.
1 group of missiles is flying northwest towards Burshtyn, Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast.
2 groups of missiles continue to fly northwest through southern Vinnytsia Oblast towards southern Khmelnytskyi Oblast.

1 group of missiles is approaching Mykolaiv, Lviv Oblast from the east.
1 group of missiles flew past Burshtyn, Ivano-Frankivsk Oblast towards Mykolaiv, Lviv Oblast.
2 groups of missiles are flying northwest towards Nova Ushytsya, Khmelnytskyi Oblast.
Explosions in Mykolaiv, Lviv Oblast. Kh-101 impacts.
The missiles in southern Khmelnytskyi Oblast have disappeared. They are either flying low, or impacted a target in that area.
The missile attack is now over. Thank you for following my coverage. I will post more details about the numbers a little later than usual while I clarify some things.
Scenes from Dnipro during the missile attack on the city. Dozens of Geran-2 drones also hit targets there earlier.
Scenes from Dnipro during the missile attack on the city. Dozens of Geran-2 drones also hit targets there earlier.

Last night, at least 15 Geran-2 drones attacked Mykolaiv City. The drones flew in three waves (6, followed by 7, followed by 2), and attacked multiple different unknown targets. Fires are now burning at the impact sites.

Scenes from Dnipro from during the drone attack (before the missiles arrived). Multiple large fires are still burning.
Scenes from Dnipro from during the drone attack (before the missiles arrived). Multiple large fires are still burning.

Ukrainian UAVs attacked the Saratov Oil Refinery in Saratov Oblast again, last night. At least 3 impacts were recorded, and fires are now burning there. 
Additionally, flights in and out of Saratov international airport were temporarily suspended.
